name: Limits
description: Contains methods that return limit information for specific resources.

getaggregatequeries().name: getAggregateQueries
getaggregatequeries().description: Returns the number of aggregate queries that have been processed with any SOQL query statement.

getlimitaggregatequeries().name: getLimitAggregateQueries
getlimitaggregatequeries().description: Returns the total number of aggregate queries that can be processed with SOQL query statements.

getcallouts().name: getCallouts
getcallouts().description: Returns the number of Web service statements that have been processed.

getchildrelationshipsdescribes().name: getChildRelationshipsDescribes
getchildrelationshipsdescribes().description: Deprecated. Returns the number of child relationship objects that have been returned.

getlimitcallouts().name: getLimitCallouts
getlimitcallouts().description: Returns the total number of Web service statements that can be processed.

getcputime().name: getCpuTime
getcputime().description: Returns the CPU time (in milliseconds) that has been used in the current transaction.

getlimitcputime().name: getLimitCpuTime
getlimitcputime().description: Returns the maximum CPU time  (in milliseconds) that can be used in a transaction.

getdmlrows().name: getDMLRows
getdmlrows().description: Returns the number of records that have been processed with any statement that counts against DML limits, such as DML statements, the Database.emptyRecycleBin method, and other methods.

getlimitdmlrows().name: getLimitDMLRows
getlimitdmlrows().description: Returns the total number of records that can be processed with any statement that counts against DML limits, such as DML statements, the database.EmptyRecycleBin method, and other methods.

getdmlstatements().name: getDMLStatements
getdmlstatements().description: Returns the number of DML statements (such as insert, update or the database.EmptyRecycleBin method) that have been called.

getlimitdmlstatements().name: getLimitDMLStatements
getlimitdmlstatements().description: Returns the total number of DML statements or the database.EmptyRecycleBin methods that can be called.

getemailinvocations().name: getEmailInvocations
getemailinvocations().description: Returns the number of email invocations (such as sendEmail) that have been called.

getlimitemailinvocations().name: getLimitEmailInvocations
getlimitemailinvocations().description: Returns the total number of email invocation (such as sendEmail) that can be called.

getfindsimilarcalls().name: getFindSimilarCalls
getfindsimilarcalls().description: Deprecated. Returns the same value as getSoslQueries. The number of findSimilar methods is no longer a separate limit, but is tracked as the number of SOSL queries issued.

getlimitfindsimilarcalls().name: getLimitFindSimilarCalls
getlimitfindsimilarcalls().description: Deprecated. Returns the same value as getLimitSoslQueries. The number of findSimilar methods is no longer a separate limit, but is tracked as the number of SOSL queries issued.

getfuturecalls().name: getFutureCalls
getfuturecalls().description: Returns the number of methods with the future annotation that have been executed (not necessarily completed).

getlimitfuturecalls().name: getLimitFutureCalls
getlimitfuturecalls().description: Returns the total number of methods with the future annotation that can be executed (not necessarily completed).

getheapsize().name: getHeapSize
getheapsize().description: Returns the approximate amount of memory (in bytes) that has been used for the heap.

getlimitheapsize().name: getLimitHeapSize
getlimitheapsize().description: Returns the total amount of memory (in bytes) that can be used for the heap.

getmobilepushapexcalls().name: getMobilePushApexCalls
getmobilepushapexcalls().description: Returns the number of Apex calls that have been used by mobile push notifications during the current metering interval.

getlimitmobilepushapexcalls().name: getLimitMobilePushApexCalls
getlimitmobilepushapexcalls().description: Returns the total number of Apex calls that are allowed per transaction for mobile push notifications.

getqueries().name: getQueries
getqueries().description: Returns the number of SOQL queries that have been issued.

getlimitqueries().name: getLimitQueries
getlimitqueries().description: Returns the total number of SOQL queries that can be issued.

getquerylocatorrows().name: getQueryLocatorRows
getquerylocatorrows().description: Returns the number of records that have been returned by the Database.getQueryLocator method.

getlimitquerylocatorrows().name: getLimitQueryLocatorRows
getlimitquerylocatorrows().description: Returns the total number of records that can be returned by the Database.getQueryLocator method.

getqueryrows().name: getQueryRows
getqueryrows().description: Returns the number of records that have been returned by issuing SOQL queries.

getlimitqueryrows().name: getLimitQueryRows
getlimitqueryrows().description: Returns the total number of records that can be returned by issuing SOQL queries.

getqueueablejobs().name: getQueueableJobs
getqueueablejobs().description: Returns the number of queueable jobs that have been added to the queue per transaction. A queueable job corresponds to a class that implements the Queueable interface.

getlimitqueueablejobs().name: getLimitQueueableJobs
getlimitqueueablejobs().description: Returns the maximum number of queueable jobs that can be added to the queue per transaction. A queueable job corresponds to a class that implements the Queueable interface.

getrunas().name: getRunAs
getrunas().description: Deprecated. Returns the same value as getDMLStatements.

getlimitrunas().name: getLimitRunAs
getlimitrunas().description: Deprecated. Returns the same value as getLimitDMLStatements.

getsavepointrollbacks().name: getSavepointRollbacks
getsavepointrollbacks().description: Deprecated. Returns the same value as getDMLStatements.

getlimitsavepointrollbacks().name: getLimitSavepointRollbacks
getlimitsavepointrollbacks().description: Deprecated. Returns the same value as getLimitDMLStatements.

getsavepoints().name: getSavepoints
getsavepoints().description: Deprecated. Returns the same value as getDMLStatements.

getlimitsavepoints().name: getLimitSavepoints
getlimitsavepoints().description: Deprecated. Returns the same value as getLimitDMLStatements.

getsoslqueries().name: getSoslQueries
getsoslqueries().description: Returns the number of SOSL queries that have been issued.

getlimitsoslqueries().name: getLimitSoslQueries
getlimitsoslqueries().description: Returns the total number of SOSL queries that can be issued.
